Welcome to ThisCausesThat! (formerly Wikicausality)
-------------------

ThisCausesThat aims to provide the users with a participatory environment where they can
identify Environmental issues and attach causal links to these issues.

Users can access the Wikipedia information and geo-tagged media associated with these issues 
and locate geographic instances of these problems on Google Maps.

We welcome you to learn about the complex webs of causality that underlie various environmental
issues and collaborate to document the likely chains of causality underlying them.